verge.com/24259381/work-home-desk-logitech-sony&quot;>;&lt;em>;David Pierce，特约编辑&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/h3>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;a93TTt&quot;>;一把舒适的办公椅&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;1Xny3W&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12447883&quot;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pZpbuA&quot;>;我只需在亚马逊上查找该名称：它是“&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06Y3PGPR2/?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;HON 办公椅黑色 |点火2.0 |符合人体工程学...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories- sale-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T18:47:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T18:47:52-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime Day 第二天您可以买到的最优惠商品</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Prime Day 期间提供的各种产品的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tm2JnOqRCfx0OYc9chLKchgFuso=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73638984/247273_Prime_Big_Deals_Days_2024_CV irginia_POST_EVENT_ROUNDUP.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您是想要一副耳机、智能家居升级、充电器还是其他东西，仍然有时间节省各种技术完全不同。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024 &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T18:44:57-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T18:44:57-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime Day 第二天的最佳耳机和耳塞优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一名男子在外面戴着索尼黑色 WH-1000XM5 降噪耳机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uGsNUdLrrgPIVN9azH6JJLZByIs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642513/DSCF7813.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;u9iLkd&quot;>;亚马逊在其推出的第二天继续提供许多最好的耳机和耳塞折扣&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;十月 Prime Day&lt;/a>; 促销。如果您想在假日购物中快速购物，或者只是想给自己一个新的升级，这是一个很好的机会。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5iYlsn&quot;>;Apple 的 AirPods Pro，即将推出获得&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/12/24241960/apple-airpods-pro-2-otc-hearing-aid-health-industry&quot;>;重要的听力健康特征&lt;/a >;，可以以优惠的价格购买，但索尼、Bose、三星也有不错的选择（例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265270/samsung-galaxy-buds-3- pro-review&quot;>;Buds 3 Pro 我刚刚评测&lt;/a>;）、Sennheiser 以及该类别中的其他中流砥柱。如果您想消除猜测，请查看我们的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds&quot;>;最佳耳塞购买指南&lt;/a>;，您会发现我最喜欢的许多产品都以诱人的价格出售。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;ufCvty&quot;>;Apple / Beats&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;88rkrD&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard: 12375646&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>;&lt;li id=&quot;6TWWYS&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Beats Studio Pro&lt;/strong>; 降噪耳机...&lt;/li>;&lt;/ul>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265995/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-earbuds-headphones-october-2024-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24265995/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-earbuds-headphones-october-2024-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24265995/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-earbuds-headphones-october-2024-sale</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T18:18:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T18:18:10-04:00</updated><title>您仍然可以以 25 美元或更少的价格购买最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6RYr3Sh-4lOtEm_1Vq2T3ifQ5uQ=/0x49:1159x822/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73643341/apple_watch_elago_w3_stand_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;现在有很多有趣的小玩意和圣诞礼物可供选择 - 包括 Elago 的 W3 Apple Watch 支架，售价低至 11.99 美元。 &lt;/em>; |图片：Elago&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;bU6gpl&quot;>;尽管您现在对食品杂货、汽油和其他必需品的价格有什么看法，但实际上您可以花不到 25 美元买到很多东西。在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;亚马逊 Prime 大优惠日等大型购物活动期间更是如此&lt;/a>;，预计今晚午夜才会结束。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;sDq5xP&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;100 美元以下可获得的最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best- Cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 促销中我们最喜欢的 50 美元以下优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得的最佳 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url &quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/ side>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;uFew5r&quot;>;距离购物只剩下几个小时了，但我们将继续在网上讨价还价箱中挖掘各种便宜的、&lt;em>;边缘&lt;/em >;-批准的技术，价格低于 25 美元。例如，现在您可以使用 &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B09B8V1LZ3?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot; 启动您的智能家居_blank&quot;>;第五代 Echo Dot&lt;/a>; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B089DR29T6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;亚马逊智能插头&lt;/a>;。需要看什么吗？标准 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Amazon-Fire-TV-Stick-4K-streaming-device/dp/B0CJM1GNFQ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target= &quot;_blank&quot;>;Fire TV Stick 4K&lt;/a>; 是流式传输无尽娱乐的绝佳渠道。或者您可以选择&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C7RPK58N/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;波斯王子：失落的王冠&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24263922/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals -under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24263922/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24263922/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-under-25-cheap-gifts-accessories-october-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T18:16:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T18:16:43-04:00</updated><title>任天堂正在接受申请加入神秘的 Switch Online 游戏测试</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;任天堂标志的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PuT2XKPNgSvj1vhDvvgqkf-Qt7g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73643339/STK054_NINTENDO_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NKEw5t&quot;>;任天堂正在邀请人们申请测试 Nintendo Switch Online 的一项新功能 - 尽管该公司没有具体说明具体内容特点是。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;T5j0yN&quot;>;考虑到这家公司刚刚推出了一款手势控制闹钟&lt;/a>;，这可能意味着任何事情，包括预览备受期待的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24051677/nintendo-switch- 2-pro-rumors-news&quot;>;切换 2&lt;/a>;。 &lt;em>;Verge &lt;/em>;工作人员的猜测涵盖了将 GameCube 游戏带到 Switch Online 上，以供 Wii 迷你复古游戏机或其他游戏机预览&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/ 9/29/16383958/star-fox-2-snes-classic-nintendo-review&quot;>;久违的《星际火狐》游戏&lt;/a>;。欢迎在评论中留下您的最佳猜测。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8gAPVM&quot;>;申请开放时间为美国东部时间 10 月 10 日星期四上午 11 点至美国东部时间 10 月 15 日星期二上午 10:59。您可以通过点击此页面上的“前往申请页面”链接&lt;a href=&quot;https://playtest-p.nintendo.com/en-us&quot;>;&lt;/a>;进行申请....&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266478/nintendo-switch-online-invite-application-beta-playtest&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266478/nintendo-switch-online-invite-application-beta-playtest" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266478/nintendo-switch-online-invite-application-beta-playtest</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T17:26:08-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T17:26:08-04:00</updated><title>互联网档案馆受到攻击，弹出窗口声称发生“灾难性”泄露</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示笔记本电脑屏幕上显示“错误”通知的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EIrUQsEXICAXSCmET4r2_FZwW9E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn。 vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73643224/akrales_220309_4977_0014.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;itUWpf&quot;>;何时周三下午，The Verge 在访问互联网档案馆 (www.archive.org) 时，看到一个弹出窗口，声称该网站已被黑客攻击。关闭消息后，网站加载正常，尽管速度很慢。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;OkzA4x&quot;>;但是，截至美国东部时间下午 5:30，该弹出窗口消失了，但网站的其余部分也消失了，只留下一条占位符消息，上面写着“互联网档案服务暂时离线”和引导访问者访问该网站的&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/internetarchive/&quot;>;X 上的帐户&lt;/a>;以获取更新。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;YRLC4w&quot;>;弹出窗口内容如下： &lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;89zInc&quot;>;“您是否曾经感觉互联网档案馆运转不稳，并且经常处于遭受灾难性安全漏洞的边缘？它就这样发生了。在 HIBP 上看到你们 3100 万人！”&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p id=&quot;KIYqxo&quot;>;HIBP 指的是&lt;a href=&quot;https://haveibeenpwned.com&quot;>;我被 Pwned 了吗？&lt;/a >;，一个人们可以查找是否...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266419/internet-archive-ddos- Attack-pop-up-message&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266419/internet-archive-ddos-attack-pop-up-message" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266419/internet-archive-ddos-attack-pop-up-message</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T17:12:16-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T17:12:16-04:00</updated><title> MacBook、iPad 等设备的 Apple Prime Day 最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上 Apple Smart Folio 中的第 10 代 iPad。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gxaU0sNHGn_aHJ6H0VoF3YPzkIM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639910/226361_Apple_iPad_10.9_10th_gen _DSeifert_0004.6.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 最新的入门级 iPad（我们对大多数人来说的第一选择）已降至 299 美元（折扣 50 美元）。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Dj3c3d&quot;>;如果您不想等到黑色星期五或网络星期一才购买一些 Apple 最受欢迎的产品，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动&lt;/a>;提供了更早的机会。目前，Apple 的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D1XD1ZV3/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第二代 AirPods Pro&lt;/ a>; 跌至历史最低点，而 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BJLXMVMV/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;最新 iPad&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CHX7R6WJ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第二代Apple Watch SE&lt;/a>; 在促销第二天仍享受大幅折扣。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;WmqF86&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;100 美元以下可获得的最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠&quot