上，“线程”的主题审核失败”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/search?q=Threads%20Moderation%20Failures&quot;>;正在流行&lt;/a>;。一些用户抱怨他们的帐户因链接到有争议主题的文章而被删除或限制。 Instagram 和 Threads 老板 Adam Mosseri &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA4aJFvvxTc&quot;>;直接回复&lt;/a>;一些投诉和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA55gP6xqMb?xmt=AQGztKVi-d95TvnowJ6kiTgIeYsxiCz_Rf5vansejAiL4Q&quot;>;说&lt;/a>;他正在“调查此事”。我是&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/Ricky_Babcock/status/1843684704182231322&quot;>;其中一个&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/IamGabeG/status/1843381623288742394&quot;>; &lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/Tiernan_Avery21/status/1843695744567652402&quot;>;很多&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/8BitShowAndTell/status/1842743495108538454&quot;>;人&lt;/a>; 谁的帐户因涉嫌是儿童而被删除 - 但我不是。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HMzBf7&quot;>;审核是社交媒体上长期存在的问题，但基于社交媒体帖子和 &lt;em >;The Verge&lt;/em>; 工作人员的亲身经历，Meta 目前正在一触即发地禁止和限制用户。我的一位同事本周&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/@kylie.robison/post/DA3i2qIPY8v&quot;>;她的帐户被短暂锁定&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.threads.net/@kylie.robison/post/DAzGBjjzFNG&quot;>;开玩笑&lt;/a>;之后，她因为热浪而“想死”。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c -float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;ks1uU2&quot;>; &lt;div class=&quot;iframely-embed&quot;>;&lt;div class=&quot;iframely-responsive&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 100%;&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA55gP6xqMb&quot; data-iframely-url=&quot;https://cdn.iframe.ly/api/iframe?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads。 net%2F%40mosseri%2Fpost%2FDA55gP6xqMb&amp;amp;key=9ef4a209439e42bc59783ba959d50197&quot;>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;XUK76q&quot;>;其他，如 Jorge... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry></feed>